&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>文本检索</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/linux-series/shell-%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ng-tech.icu/books/linux-series/shell-%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86/%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="文本检索">文本检索&lt;/h1>
